<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>결제 취소 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f3ef;
      color: #111;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    p { color: #666; line-height: 1.7; }
    .info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #efe9df;
      border-radius: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .actions {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .dark { background: #111; color: #fff; }
    .light { background: #efe9df; color: #111; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>결제가 취소되었습니다</h1>
      <p>아직 결제가 완료되지 않았기 때문에 주문은 결제취소 상태로만 남고, 재고 차감도 없습니다.</p>

      <div class="info">
        주문번호: <strong><%= order._id %></strong><br />
        merchantUid: <strong><%= order.merchantUid %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="dark" href="/order">주문서로 돌아가기</a>
        <a class="light" href="/">메인으로 가기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>